<h1 class="text-4xl text-center font-serif mb-8 hinge-header">
  Our Story
</h1>

<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  Our story, like so many of the modern age, began on the dating app Hinge.
  While enjoying the holidays with her family, Helen vented to her
  sisters: "I'm only meeting people of low quality and I don't know why!"
  Susan and Karen, always there to be Helen's guiding compass, took
  a look at her profile and were apalled by what they found.
</p>
<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  "No wonder you're only matching with miscreants. A profile like this is no
  good! You've got to accurately display yourself and put the energy out
  there that you want to find &mdash; a nerdy, active, honest person."
  Unable to tolerate the mess of misrepresentation before them, Susan and Karen joined forces.
  Together they channeled the power of sisterhood and their lifelong love of Helen's essence to perform a Cinderellian transformation of
  Helen's Hinge profile.
</p>

<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  Naught but a few days later, Helen liked
  the profile of a dashing young nerd named Adam. Our first conversation
  went like this:
</p>

